section_title: Accelerating Energy Efficiency Action in Urban Environments
sentences: The TEM on accelerating energy efficiency action in urban environments took place on Friday, 5 June, and Saturday, 6 June.
For a summary of the TEM, see: http://www.iisd.ca/vol12/enb12633e.html and http://www.iisd.ca/vol12/enb12634e.html
